
Original project was http://log4go.googlecode.com/.

Added features:
- Close method waits for all loggers to complete
- Added configuration for limiting log file size and number of files 

Installation:
- Run `go get github.com/hummerd/hummerdk-log4go`

Usage:
- Add the following import:
import l4g "log4go.googlecode.com/hg"

Acknowledgements:
- pomack
  For providing awesome patches to bring log4go up to the latest Go spec
